name: Duck to the Humor
description:
An intelligent duck named Duck with 420 IQ ran away from a lab at deep ocean. He's going up to the surface..

Non sense game by a/t-jam (zaryanz and toyboot4e) for Jame Gam jam in 2021 (theme: Duck, feature: Abyss). Source code repository

Credits:

  • ebiten: The 2D game library in Go
  • Greysen Johnson: Background images
  • Gilgaphoenixignis: Enemy image
  • kotnaszynce: Duck image
  • ザ・マッチメイカァズ (THE MATCH-MAKERS): Attack/death sound
  • On-Jin ～音人～: Bubble/encounter/win sound
  • ぴぽや (Pipoya): Attack animation
